"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     Farrell JJ. Digestion and absorption of nutrients and vitamins. In: Sleisenger and Fordtran's Gastrointestinal and Liver Disease, 9th ed, Feldman M, Friedman L, Brandt L (Eds), Saunders, Philadelphia, PA 2010. p.1695.",
"    </li>",
